sequenceDiagram
    participant Manager
    participant Dashboard
    participant Queue
    participant Database
    participant Analytics
    participant Notifications
    participant Colegio
    participant Perito

    Note over Manager,Perito: Work Queue + Analytics Flow

    Manager->>Dashboard: Create avalúo
    Dashboard->>Queue: POST request
    Queue->>Database: Insert record
    Database-->>Queue: ID + timestamp
    Queue->>Analytics: Log creation event
    Queue-->>Dashboard: Success
    Dashboard-->>Manager: Confirmation

    Manager->>Dashboard: View available Colegios
    Dashboard->>Queue: GET colegios
    Queue->>Analytics: Request workload data
    Analytics->>Database: Query metrics
    Database-->>Analytics: Stats
    Analytics-->>Queue: Enriched data
    Queue-->>Dashboard: Colegio list
    Dashboard-->>Manager: Show with indicators

    Manager->>Dashboard: Assign to Colegio
    Dashboard->>Queue: PUT assign
    Queue->>Database: Update avalúo
    Queue->>Analytics: Log assignment
    Queue->>Notifications: Send alert
    Notifications->>Colegio: New assignment
    Queue-->>Dashboard: Confirmed
    Dashboard-->>Manager: Success

    Colegio->>Dashboard: View dashboard
    Dashboard->>Queue: GET assignments
    Queue->>Database: Query data
    Queue->>Analytics: Get team metrics
    Analytics->>Database: Calculate workload
    Database-->>Analytics: Team stats
    Analytics-->>Queue: Dashboard data
    Queue-->>Dashboard: Assignments + metrics
    Dashboard-->>Colegio: Show queue

    Colegio->>Dashboard: Check Perito availability
    Dashboard->>Analytics: Request capacity
    Analytics->>Database: Query active cases
    Database-->>Analytics: Workload per Perito
    Analytics-->>Dashboard: Availability matrix
    Dashboard-->>Colegio: Show Perito list

    Colegio->>Dashboard: Assign to Perito
    Dashboard->>Queue: PUT assign perito
    Queue->>Database: Update records
    Queue->>Analytics: Log event
    Queue->>Notifications: Alert Perito
    Notifications->>Perito: Assignment notification
    Queue-->>Dashboard: Success
    Dashboard-->>Colegio: Updated view

    Perito->>Dashboard: Update status
    Dashboard->>Queue: PATCH status
    Queue->>Database: Update status
    Queue->>Analytics: Log change
    Analytics->>Database: Recalculate KPIs

    Manager->>Dashboard: View analytics
    Dashboard->>Analytics: GET metrics
    Analytics->>Database: Query events
    Database-->>Analytics: Raw data
    Note over Analytics: Process metrics<br/>Calculate KPIs<br/>Generate trends
    Analytics-->>Dashboard: Compiled data
    Dashboard-->>Manager: Charts and reports

    Perito->>Dashboard: Submit completion
    Dashboard->>Queue: PUT complete
    Queue->>Database: Update status
    Queue->>Analytics: Log completion
    Analytics->>Database: Calculate SLA
    Queue->>Notifications: Notify Manager
    Notifications->>Manager: Completion alert
    Queue-->>Dashboard: Success
    Dashboard-->>Perito: Confirmed

    Note over Analytics,Database: Daily batch processing<br/>Historical trends<br/>Performance reports
